Package com.pom.crimson.testcases.explore.medium

Contains Test classes for Testing Medium priority Explore modules in the mobile app.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExplorePageBasedOnGroupsSectionTest
    This test class contains test cases for Explore Page or Content page (for Based on Groups section only).
    Explore Page or Content page displays articles and videos as per user's interests and joined groups.
    HomePageCardTest
    This test class contains test cases for Daily tips to be displayed on Home Page.
    Daily tips are currently displayed for Parent to be and New parent archetypes only.
    For Parent to be : It displays as per due date.
